    options: ['Fresco', 'Tempera', 'Oil paint', 'Encaustic'],
    answer: 3,
  },
  {
    category: 'Gallery',
    q: 'Vermeer\'s "Girl with a Pearl Earring" is classified in Dutch painting as what type of work?',
