    category: 'Gallery',
    q: '"Las Meninas" (1656), one of art history\'s most analyzed paintings, was created by which Spanish master?',
    options: ['Francisco Goya', 'El Greco', 'Bartolomé Murillo', 'Diego Velázquez'],
    answer: 3,
